# flipkart-ecommrance
# 🛒 Flipkart E-Commerce Clone

A responsive **Flipkart-inspired E-Commerce website** built using **HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Node.js, and Express.js**. This project recreates the basic shopping experience with multiple product categories and user authentication pages.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🏠 Home Page
- 👕 Fashion Section
- 📱 Mobiles Section
- 💻 Electronics Section
- 📺 TV Section
- 🛋 Furniture Section
- 📦 Products Page
- 🔐 User Login
- 📝 User Signup
- ⚡ Responsive Design
- 🌐 Express.js Backend

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

### Frontend
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js

### Tools
- Git
- GitHub
- VS Code

