## ⚙️ Installation

### Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/flipkart-ecommerce.git
```

### Navigate into Project

```bash
cd flipkart-ecommerce
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### Start Server

```bash
node server.js
```

or

```bash
nodemon server.js
```

